{"tid":697202,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"而家班樓市淡友唔比人唱好，一唱好就話你買左樓。","createTime":"2018-06-10T18:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T00:12:32.000Z","uid":103799,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fceb1b5c27646a6401f3d2ee465f37cfeccda2da","tid":697202,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:51:23.000Z","msg":"我開幾個post, 就話我一味要唱好，話我買左樓，又咩又柒。<br />\n係咪痴左線。<br />\n<br />\n你唔分析你嘅事，人地分析就話人係有樓硬唱好。<br />\n死牛一面頸<br />\n<br />\n我係因為諗返轉頭，一早入左市果班，我以前以為佢地會輸到七彩，點知而家個個賺左幾百萬，我要儲幾耐先儲到。  <br />\n事實我係睇錯左，我已經輸左。<br />\n錯失左黃金機會。<br />\n<br />\n發現好多淡友覺得呢2句係真理，神聖不可侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n1.市場有升一定有跌(鬼唔知阿媽女人，30年先跌你等唔等到)<br />\n2.咁多人睇好個市即係要爆(都已經睇好左好多年，愈嚟愈多人睇好其實係咪即係會升）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係果句，如果我已經，或者我買過樓，我終生乞食。<br />\n如果我講真話我變富翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341ae1acb14c42c08244e986c030abb15d8b580c","tid":697202,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:58:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b2c9c6cce97ab9bd31d1f0ff7669a8b6bd81ede","tid":697202,"uid":35101,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:59:47.000Z","msg":"留名上熱門"},{"pid":"b4568e1d33189b77d46abc33b29bcaeb67badde5","tid":697202,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"341ae1acb14c42c08244e986c030abb15d8b580c","tid":697202,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:58:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T19:00:05.000Z","msg":"唔識，錯就認，打就企定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2b9b7161c407be3db47065708c3a8bc1fc4c0e","tid":697202,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"This post must fire <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1720a2c3493b2acbac30d8074af35a4c325de96",